summary: Adds a hand-drawn Stormcloak tat to female bodies on/around the left breast.
descriptionHtml:
This tat mod requires you have Calientes Female Body Mod Big Bottom Edition -CBBE- by Caliente (http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=2666) installed first.

Adds my Dovahkiin Stormcloak logo as a medium chest tat on female models using CBBE. Has a very realistic skin texture to it similar to real tattoo textures. Simply extract and copy/cut and past the texture into skyrim/data/textures/actors/character/female.
author: FXtreme
